Package homeworks.hw1

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MyStack<T>
    MyStack is a simple class that implements a stack abstraction.
    MyStackClient
    A client program for MyStack.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    StackSize
    A simple enum used by MyStack(int, StackSize) to determine the inner representation of MyStack instances.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidCapacityException
    InvalidCapacityException instances are thrown from MyStack(int, StackSize) when the user provides a non-positive capacity for the MyStack instance.
